ot;赞助nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;&lt;em>;塞尔达传说：王国之泪&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>;，甚至使用 &lt;a href 等摄像头来提升您的家庭安全水平=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Blink-Video-Doorbell/dp/B08SGKLDRV?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;闪烁视频门铃&lt;/a>;或&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/introducing-the-all-new-Ring-Indoor-Cam/dp/B0B6GLQJMV?tag=theverge02 -20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;环形室内摄像头&lt;/a>;。许多优惠也可以成为很棒的圣诞礼物，或者作为一种简单的方式......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24306407/black-friday- 2024-best-deals-under-30-tech-gift-ideas-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24306407/black-friday-2024-best-deals-under-30-tech-gift-ideas-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24306407/black-friday-2024-best-deals-under-30-tech-gift-ideas-cyber-monday</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-02T12:45:07-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-02T12:45:07-05:00</updated><title>泄密揭示了一款具有紧凑折叠设计的新型 DJI 无人机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;联邦通信委员会文件披露的新型 DJI Flip 无人机的插图和详细信息。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1jsK0Ok_BLbVaqI1KrdfHZtmBxE=/0x0:1628x1085/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73761029/DJI_flip1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;新泄露的视频和 FCC 文件揭示了一款新的 DJI 紧凑型折叠无人机。&lt;/em>; |屏幕截图：FCC&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;DzyHNB&quot;>;DJI 紧凑型折叠无人机系列的下一款产品已在泄露的图像、视频和 FCC 文件中披露。新款 DJI Flip 具有类似于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236503/dji-neo-vs-hoverair-selfie-drone-specs-price-hands-on&quot;>; 的螺旋桨护罩DJI Neo&lt;/a>;，将采用类似于&lt;a的折叠设计href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24211113/hoverair-x1-review-selfie-drone-price-specs&quot;>;HoverAir X1&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/jasperellens/status/1863148746206322729?s=61&amp;amp;t=xYOFFBlYQ3CcTJv951NYFA&quot;>;根据可靠泄密者&lt;/a>; Jasper Ellens 在 X 上分享的视频。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;EhC7Nk&quot;>;大疆目前的折叠无人机，包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/25/23890019/dji-mini-4-pro-price-release-date&quot;>;Mini 4 Pro&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2022/12/9/23501450/dji-mini-3-drone-announcement-price-date&quot;>;Mini 3&lt;/a>;，功能折叠的螺旋桨和手臂向每架无人机身体的两侧折叠。在泄露的动画中，DJI Flip 上的防护螺旋桨似乎向下折叠，导致所有四个螺旋桨整齐地堆叠在一起，以帮助使无人机更小，并且在不飞行时更容易运输。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot; MWItDZ&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot; data-dnt=&quot;true&quot;align=&quot;center&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;突发：感谢我的朋友 YueYue，这是.. .&lt;/p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311063/dji-flip-folding-drone-fcc-leak&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311063/dji-flip-folding-drone-fcc-leak" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311063/dji-flip-folding-drone-fcc-leak</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-02T12:43:29-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-02T12:43:29-05:00</updated><title> Google 地图现在显示位智事件报告</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Google 地图徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2swaeglAdxXw_Efm1LHyFeFr1Co=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73761021/STK270_GOOGLE_MAPS_D.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZL86pr&quot;>;Google 地图现在开始在您导航时显示 Waze 事件报告，并包括通过确认道路状况来做出贡献的功能应用程序通过提示。 Google &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/31/24209969/google-maps-destination-guidance-waze-camera-events&quot;>;于 7 月宣布&lt;/a>;这两款应用将交叉传播更多数据，将更多 Waze 来源的道路封闭、施工、超速摄像头和警察存在信息传送到 Google 地图中。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;6rXw4y&quot;>;据 &lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5google.com/2024/11/30/google-maps-waze-reports/&quot;>;&lt;em>;9to5Google&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 报道和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.androidauthority.com/google-maps-waze-reports-3504512/&quot;>;&lt;em>;Android Authority&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，在假期周末，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/GoogleMaps/comments/1h38vj1/google_maps_now_sharing_waze_user_reports/?rdt=57396&quot;>;一位 Reddit 用户&lt;/a>;分享了一张提示屏幕截图，显示“警方提前报告”，基于位智司机的报告。与地图中的其他事件通知一样，用户可以更新报告以记录是否仍然看到相同的内容。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Reddit 用户 &lt;a class= “ql-link”href =“https://www.reddit.com/r/GoogleMaps/comments/1h38vj1/google_maps_now_sharing_waze_user_reports/?rdt=57396” target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Truckin_18&lt;/a>;&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;非常 Waze-y...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311129/google-map-waze-integration-incident-reporting-rollout&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311129/google-map-waze-integration-incident-reporting-rollout" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311129/google-map-waze-integration-incident-reporting-rollout</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-02T12:39:34-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-02T12:39:34-05:00</updated><title>您现在可以获得的顶级网络星期一优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;浏览器窗口中排列的网络星期一销售产品的插图。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eN-C8Y4oBM5R56F-wkCPw4_952g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cd n.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73756741/247350_CMBF_2024_EWinatacyberMonday.6.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Elen Winata for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;现在是购买各种 Verge 认可的商品的好时机，包括智能手表、流媒体和亚马逊最新的 Kindle。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24309106/best-black-friday-deals-2024-tech-gadgets-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24309106/best-black-friday-deals-2024-tech-gadgets-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24309106/best-black-friday-deals-2024-tech-gadgets-cyber-monday</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-02T12:37:32-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-02T12:37:32-05:00</updated><title>苹果在新诉讼中被指控窥探员工的 iPhone</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LJzDjBGLHyiQAdD5vB8yKyXHqno=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73761009/STK071_APPLE_E.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;pxWdPR&quot;>;一名苹果员工正在起诉该公司，指控该公司要求员工放弃隐私权并使他们受到监视， &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.semafor.com/article/12/02/2024/employee-lawsuit-accuses-apple-of-spying-on-its-workers&quot;>;首先由&lt;em>;Semafor&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;报道。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/25429066-apple-employee-complaint?responsive=1&amp;amp;title=1&quot;>;周一提起的诉讼&lt;/a>;中，苹果员工 Amar Bhakta 指控苹果通过公司管理的设备访问员工数据——包括“积极鼓励”员工使用个人 iPhone。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ctfGDd&quot;>;尽管苹果为员工提供了以下选择：诉讼称，苹果敦促用户携带自己的 iPhone 上班，并由苹果内部软件管理。根据公司政策，与这些 Apple 管理的设备关联的数据（包括电子邮件、照片、视频、笔记和其他信息）“将受到 Apple 的搜索”...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311060/apple-employee-surveillance-lawsuit&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311060/apple-employee-surveillance-lawsuit" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311060/apple-employee-surveillance-lawsuit</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-02T12:31:37-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-02T12:31:37-05:00</updated><title> Garmin Forerunner 255 于网络星期一发售</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;女士手腕上的 Garmin Forerunner 255S&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NZ3cFgys0g71bMZPnEltl13ISqo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73760997/IMG_0264.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Garmin Forerunner 255 网络星期一优惠 100 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;uw7V99&quot;>;Garmins 的价格相当可观。但对于寻求优惠的跑步者来说，这是个好消息：优秀的 Forerunner 255 在网络星期一降至 250 美元（折扣 100 美元）。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;D8yEE0&quot;>;虽然它是最新一代设备，但 Forerunner 255 将会吸引那些喜欢尽可能长的电池寿命的跑步者。这是因为它具有像素内存显示屏，这意味着一次充电可持续使用 14 天。 MIP 显示屏在阳光直射下也更容易阅读。有&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23632332/garmin-forerunner-265s-review-oled-smartwatch-running&quot;>;较新的 265 型号&lt;/a>;，但它有一个 OLED 显示屏，电池续航时间略短，为 13 天。鉴于 Garmin 似乎热衷于将其大部分产品线转向 OLED，因此这是在库存仍然可用的情况下抢购 MIP 跑步手表的好机会。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;PH5nC4&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component =&quot;productcard:12495837&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;H8whr5&quot;>;另一个巧妙的福利是 255 是最...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311166/cyber-monday-garmin-forerunner-255-deals&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311166/cyber-monday-garmin-forerunner-255-deals" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311166/cyber-monday-garmin-forerunner-255-deals</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-12-02T12:13:45-05:00</published><updated> 2024-12-02T12:13:45-05:00</updated><title>谷歌废弃的 Pixel Tablet 2 拥有更好的显示屏和 5G 升级</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一只手拿着原始 Pixel 平板电脑。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/l6sggKV1_u0C9m0nQDbyCWGK7Og=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.v ox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73760922/236705_Google_Pixel_Tablet_DSeifert_0014.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;最初的 Pixel 平板电脑只有 60Hz 显示屏。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zz1fkU&quot;>;Pixel Tablet 2 可能会&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/21/24302508 /google-pixel-tablet-2-canceled-rumor&quot;>;永远见不到曙光&lt;/a>;，但有新的详细信息&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.androidauthority.com/exclusive-canceled-pixel-tablet-2-3504100/&quot;>;Android Authority 的报告揭示了 Google 可能已经采取了哪些措施大二设备的套子，包括高刷新显示屏、5G 连接等。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;PRSGKN&quot;>;Tablet 2 显然将配备 120Hz 10.95 英寸 LCD 显示屏，刷新率是其前身的两倍，而分辨率则保持在 2,560 x 1,600 像素不变。 Tablet 2 也进行了一些相机升级：它将配备与 Pixel 9 Pro Fold 相同的 10MP 自拍相机，并且 Google 还用 11MP 射手更新了后置摄像头。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;9AZnIi&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Google Pixel 平板电脑评测：底座使所有Difference&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23765921/google-pixel-tablet-review&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;据报道，Google 取消了 Pixel Tablet 2，并可能退出该类别 -再次&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/21/24302508/google-pixel-tablet-2-canceled-rumor&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;LhCMEt&quot;>;据报道，谷歌还计划从 Pixel 9 系列引入 5G 调制解调器，不过具有蜂窝连接功能的 Tablet 2 型号将...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311118/google-canceled-pixel-tablet-2-better-display-5g-tensor-g4&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311118/google-canceled-pixel-tablet-2-better-display-5g-tensor-g4" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/12/2/24311118/google-canceled-pixel-tablet-2-better-display-5g-tensor-g4</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry></feed>